        Selling Your Home with Pets in Brisbane: Practical Tips
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Practical, non-judgmental advice on managing pets during open homes, photography, and the sale campaign.
      </p>
